  <thing id="iBulwaLive" name="Bulwark of the Living" description="{b}Price (Item Level){/b}: 10,157 gp (12th level) \n{b}Body Slot{/b}: &#151;(held) \n{b}Caster Level{/b}: 7th \n{b}Aura{/b}: Moderate (DC 18); necromancy \n{b}Activation{/b}: &#151; and standard (command) \n{b}Weight{/b}: 10 lb. \n\n{i}This heavy wooden shield is perfectly spherical and rimmed in mithral. The sun disk of Pelor is emblazoned across its surface. {/i}\n\nA good-aligned character who bears this +1 {i}blinding heavy wooden shield{/i} can expend a 4th-level or higher divine spell as a standard action to cast {i}death ward{/i} (PH 217) on himself. \n\n{i}Cost to Create{/i}: 5,000 gp (plus 157 gp for masterwork heavy wooden shield), 400 XP, 10 days. \n\n{i}Prerequisites{/i}: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, death ward, {i}searing light{/i}, good alignment.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="MagicArmor">
