    </thing>
  <thing id="iStaffVaga" name="Staff of the Vagabond" description="{b}Price (Item Level){/b}: 3,600 gp (8th)\n{b}Body Slot{/b}: &#151; (held)\n{b}Caster Level{/b}: 9th\n{b}Aura{/b}: Moderate (DC 19); conjuration\n{b}Activation{/b}: &#151;\n{b}Weight{/b}: 2 lb.\n\n{i}This battered, weatherbeaten stick looks far too flimsy and brittle to be usable as a quarterstaff&#151;or even as a walking stick.{/i}\n\nThis masterwork/masterwork quarterstaff becomes a +1/+1 {i}quarterstaff{/i} as long as you are carrying no other weapons. (Natural weapons or unarmed attacks don&apos;t count, but weapons you carry in a {i}bag of holding{/i} or other container do. )\n\nThe {i}staff of the vagabond{/i} is part of a set known collectively as the {i}garb of the vagabond{/i}, which also includes the {i}cloak of the vagabond{/i}, the {i}robe of the vagabond{/i}, and the {i}sandals of the vagabond{/i}. When you wield the {i}staff of the vagabond{/i} while wearing any two of the other items, each end gains the merciful property (DMG 225). When you wield it while wearing all three of the other items, each end also gains the ki focus property (DMG 225).\n\n{i}Cost to Create{/i}: 1,500 gp (plus 600 gp for masterwork/masterwork quarterstaff), 120 XP, 3 days.\n\n{i}Prerequisites{/i}: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}cure light wounds{/i}, monk.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="MagicWep">
    <comment>Script to mod name if wearing other set members and show the special when modded. (Done)

Page 137 &#150; Staff of the Vagabond
[Substitution]
The school should be conjuration,
not transmutation.</comment>
