  <thing id="ioBeastMan" name="Mantle of the Beast" description="{b}Price (Item Level){/b}: 18,000 gp (14th)\n{b}Body Slot{/b}: Shoulders\n{b}Caster Level{/b}: 10th\n{b}Aura{/b}: Moderate (DC 20); transmutation\n{b}Activation{/b}: &#151;\n{b}Weight{/b}: 2 lb.\n\n{i}This heavy cloak is made of a rough, gray fur from some unidentifiable creature.{/i}\n\nThe {i}mantle of the beast{/i} allows you to use your wild shape ability as a swift action. While wild shaped, your natural weapons gain a +1 enhancement bonus on attack and damage rolls, giving you a magic weapon for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.\n\nA {i}mantle of the beast{/i} is part of a set known collectively as the {i}trappings of the beast{/i}, which also includes the {i}armor of the beast{/i} (page 135) and the {i}ring of the beast{/i} (see below). When you wear all three items together, you gain additional abilities, as noted in the description of {i}armor of the beast{/i}.\n\n{i}Cost to Create{/i}: 9,000 gp, 720 XP, 18 days.\n\n{i}Prerequisites{/i}: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}greater magic fang{/i}, wild shape.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Wondrous">
