  <thing id="ioQuiElven" name="Quiver of Elvenkind" description="{b}Price (Item Level){/b}: 8,000 gp (11th) \n{b}Body Slot{/b}: &#151; \n{b}Caster Level{/b}: 12th \n{b}Aura{/b}: Strong (DC 21); necromancy\n{b}Activation{/b}: &#151; \n{b}Weight{/b}: 7 lb. \n\n{i}Made of soft brown leather, this quiver has been expertly stitched with golden strands. A tiny image of an eye is etched into its strap. {/i}\n\nA {i}quiver of elvenkind{/i} holds up to 50 arrows. Any nonmagical arrow drawn forth from the quiver functions as a +1 {i}arrow{/i} (as long as it has been held in the quiver for at least the previous hour). This magic fades after 1 round. \n\nIf you are an elf or a worshiper of Corellon Larethian, however, any nonmagical arrow drawn from the quiver functions instead as a +1 {i}orc bane arrow{/i}, and on a critical hit permanently blinds any living target (Fortitude DC 14 negates). \n\nIf you are an elf using this quiver in conjunction with a {i}bow of elvenkind{/i} (page 137), you gain additional benefits as noted in the description of that item. \n\n{i}Cost to Create{/i}: 4,000 gp, 320 XP, 8 days. \n\n{i}Prerequisites{/i}: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, Craft Wondrous Item, {i}blindness{/i}, elf.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Wondrous">
