  <thing id="xCresValor" name="Crest of Valor" description="While wearing a {i}crest of valor{/i}, you gain a +2 morale bonus on melee weapon damage rolls while your current hit point total is equal to or less than one-half of your full normal hit points.\n\nThe {i}crest of valor{/i} is part of a set known collectively as the {i}raiment of valor{/i}, which also includes the {i}periapt of valor{/i} (page 140) and the {i}tabard of valor{/i} (page 142). When wearing all three of these items, all allies within 10 feet of you (including yourself) gain a +4 morale bonus on saves against fear effects." compset="Special" summary="+2 morale bon to melee dam when at 1/2 Hp or less.">
