  <thing id="xPeriValor" name="Periapt of Valor" description="While wearing a {i}periapt of valor{/i}, you gain a +2 morale bonus on AC and saving throws while your current hit point total is equal to or less than one-half of your full normal hit points.\n\nThe {i}periapt of valor{/i} is part of a set known collectively as the {i}raiment of valor{/i}. When you wear it along with a {i}crest of valor{/i} (page 139) and a {i}tabard of valor{/i} (page 142), you gain additional abilities as given in the description of the {i}crest of valor{/i}." compset="Special" summary="+2 morale bon to AC and saves when at 1/2 Hp or less.">
    <tag group="Helper" tag="SpSourceEq"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="xTabaValor" name="Tabard of Valor" description="Whenever your current hit point total is equal to or less than one-half of your full normal hit points, you gain the mettle ability: If you are affected by a spell that would normally have a reduced effect on a successful Fortitude or Will saving throw, it instead has no effect at all upon you if you save successfully. If you already have mettle from a class feature or some other source, you instead gain improved mettle, which halves the harmful effects of a spell on a failed Fortitude or Will save while still protecting you entirely on a successful save.\n\nThe {i}tabard of valor{/i} is part of a set known collectively as the {i}raiment of valor{/i}, which also includes the {i}crest of valor{/i} (page 139) and the {i}periapt of valor{/i} (page 140). When you use a tabard with both of the other items, you gain additional abilities, as noted in the description of the {i}crest of valor{/i}." compset="Special" summary="Gain mettle ability when at 1/2 Hp or less.">
    <tag group="Helper" tag="SpSourceEq"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="xRaimValor" name="Raiment of Valor" description="When wearing all three of the raiment of valor&apos;s items, all allies within 10 feet of you (including yourself) gain a +4 morale bonus on saves against fear effects." compset="Special" summary="You and all allies within 10 ft gain +4 bonus on saves vs fear.">
