  <thing id="sClrSouWar" name="Soul Ward" description="{i}Your comrade&apos;s thoughts and feelings meld with yours, each bolstering the other, through the touch of your hand.{/i} \n\nThis spell functions like {i}body ward{/i} (page 117), except that you choose one of the three mental abilities&#151;Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma&#151;rather than a physical ability to be affected." compset="Spell" summary="Subject is protected against 5 points of ability damage to Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma; repeated use for different scores also increases damage absorbed.">
