  <thing id="sPalTouRes" name="Touch of Restoration" description="{i}When you pray for the power to restore that which your friend has lost, a beam of sun breaks through the clouds and bathes your hands in golden light.{/i} \n\nCasting {i}touch of restoration{/i} lets you use your lay on hands ability to cure ability damage. While this spell is active, you can cure 1 point of ability damage per caster level by laying on hands, and you can split these points among different creatures if desired." compset="Spell" summary="Use part of your lay on hands ability to cure 1 point of ability damage.">
