  <thing id="sBlkWarMou" name="War-Mount" description="{i}At your touch, your mount&apos;s flanks ripple, and its eyes blaze with new-found energy.{/i} \n\nYou render the natural attacks of your mount or fiendish companion magical with a touch. The creature gains a +2 enhancement bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls with its natural weapons for the duration of the spell. They are treated as both magic and good-aligned (paladin) or evil-aligned (blackguard) weapons for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction. \n\nIf you cast this spell in conjunction with {i}master cavalier{/i} (page 124) and {i}phantom charge{/i} (page 125), the three spells have a synergistic effect. See the {i}master cavalier{/i} spell description for details." compset="Spell" summary="Your mount gains a +2 enhancement bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls with its natural weapons; use with other spells grants mount fly speed.">
