  <thing id="sPalConLif" name="Conduit of Life" description="{i}A small kernel of positive energy grows within your heart, warming your whole body. {/i}\n\nThe next time you use a class feature or racial ability to channel positive energy (such as turn undead or lay on hands), you also heal a number of points of damage to yourself equal to 2d10+1/caster level (maximum 10). \n\nIf you are already subject to an ongoing healing effect (such as {i}vigor{/i}), or if you receive a {i}cure{/i} spell while {i}conduit of life{/i} is still in effect, this spell instead heals a number of points of damage equal to 3d8+1/caster level (maximum +10) and it is discharged." compset="Spell" summary="Heal 2d10+1/caster level (max. 10) points of damage to yourself while channeling positive energy.">
