Cold resistance 5 \nWee Jas&#150;&#150;&#150;&#150;Spell resistance 13 \nYondalla&#150;&#150;&#150;&#150;Shadow and silent moves" compset="Spell" summary="Your shield or armor gains a +1 enhancement bonus plus a special ability that varies by deity.">
