    <exprreq message="Wild Shape required."><![CDATA[hero.tagis[Hero.WildShape] <> 0]]></exprreq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fCharMia" name="Charnel Miasma" description="Your close connection to death magic causes others to find your company unpleasant.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Access to the Death domain.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have a 2nd-level or higher Death domain spell available to cast, you exude an almost imperceptible scent of the grave wherever you go. As a standard action, you can force one foe within 30 feet to attempt a Will save or be shaken for 1 minute. If you use this ability on an already shaken creature and it fails its saving throw, it becomes panicked for 1 minute or until it spends 1 full round out of line of sight of you. Creatures that succeed on this save are not affected again by your charnel miasma for 24 hours.\n\nAs a secondary benefit, you gain a +1 competence bonus to your caster level when casting death spells.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="Death dom spl 2nd+, stand, 1 foe in 30 ft shaken/panicked 1 min (Will neg)." uniqueness="useronce">
