  <thing id="fHolyWarr" name="Holy Warrior" description="Your zeal on the battlefield allows you to deal extra damage in combat.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 4th-level spells, access to the War domain.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have a 4th-level or higher War domain spell available to cast, you gain a bonus on your weapon damage rolls equal to the level of the highest-level War spell you have available to cast.\n\nAs a secondary benefit, you gain a +1 competence bonus to your caster level when casting force spells.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="War domain spl 4th+, add spl level as bon to weapon damage." uniqueness="useronce">
