  <thing id="fSpontDom" name="Spontaneous Domains" description="You need not prepare your domain spells in advance.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 3rd-level spells, access to two or more cleric domains.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When preparing your spells for the day, you can leave your domain slots open. You can then choose, when the situation arises, to cast any of the domain spells you could normally have prepared for a given level. However, you are still limited to one domain spell per level per day.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Clerics must prepare their domain spells before casting.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="Can leave domain slots open and use to spont cast one of your domain spells." uniqueness="useronce">
