validif (tagcount[Hero.Arcane] >= 3 + 1)]]></validate>
      </prereq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fStrDev" name="Strength Devotion" description="You can overcome an opponent&apos;s normal resistance to damage.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Once per day as a swift action, you can bypass hardness with your melee attacks for 1 minute. In addition, you gain a slam attack as a natural weapon, and all your melee attacks (natural or not) gain the adamantine property for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.\n\nAs a natural weapon, your slam attack does not provoke attacks of opportunity. It deals damage based on your size and character level, as given on the following table.\n\nCharacter Level          Damage (S)        Damage (M)        Damage (L)\n1st-5th                                1d4                       1d6                      1d8\n6th-10th                              1d6                       1d8                      2d6\n11th-15th                            1d8                      1d10                    2d8\n16th-20th                           1d10                      2d6                     3d6\n \nIf you already have a natural weapon, use whichever damage value is higher. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus on any damage rolls you make with that weapon.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You can select this feat multiple times, gaining one additional daily use each time you take it.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: If you have the ability to turn or rebuke undead, you gain one additional daily use of hits feat for each daily turn or rebuke use you expend.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat">
    <usesource source="CompChamp" parent="p35" name="Complete Champion"/>
    <tag group="fCategory" tag="Domain"/>
    <bootstrap thing="xStrDevote">
      <autotag group="wMain" tag="1d6_5"/>
      </bootstrap>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fSwiftCal" name="Swift Call" description="You can call your special mount in the blink of an eye.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Special mount class feature.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can call your special mount as a swift action.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Calling a special mount is a full-round action.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="Calling special mount is reduced to a swift action." uniqueness="useronce">
    <usesource source="CompChamp" parent="p35" name="Complete Champion"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="ShowSpec"/>
    <tag group="fCategory" tag="General"/>
    <exprreq message="Special Mount required."><![CDATA[hero.tagis[CompAvail.cPalMount] <> 0]]></exprreq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fSwiftWS" name="Swift Wild Shape" description="You can shift forms in the blink of an eye.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Dex 13, Fast Wild Shape, wild shape class feature.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can activate your wild shape ability as a swift action.\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Activating wild shape is a standard action.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="Wild shape is reduced to a swift action." uniqueness="useronce">
    <usesource source="CompChamp" parent="p35" name="Complete Champion"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="ShowSpec"/>
    <tag group="fCategory" tag="Wild"/>
    <exprreq message="Dexterity 13 required."><![CDATA[child[aDEX].field[aFinalVal].value >= 13]]></exprreq>
    <exprreq message="Fast Wild Shape required."><![CDATA[#hasfeat[fFastWldSh] <> 0]]></exprreq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fTouchHe" name="Touch of Healing" description="You can channel divine energy into healing with a touch.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 2nd-level spells.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have a conjuration (healing) spell of 2nd level or higher available cast, you can spend a standard action to touch a target creature and heal 3 points of damage per level of the highest-level conjuration (healing) spell you have available to cast. You can use this ability only on a target that has been reduce to one-half or fewer of its total hit points. The effect ends once you&apos;ve healed the subject up to half its normal maximum hit points. This ability has no effect on creatures that can&apos;t be healed by {i}cure{/i} spells.\n\nAs a secondary benefit, you gain a +1 competence bonus to your caster level when casting conjuration (healing) spells.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="Conjuration (healing) 2nd+, touch heals 3 x spl lvl, must be less than 1/2 Hp." uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Modified Eval Script to add 1 to the zzConjHeal Thing created for the Healer class.  This new Thing was needed to track the different adjustments to caster levels.


Pre req (Done)</comment>
    <usesource source="CompChamp" parent="p35" name="Complete Champion"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="ShowSpec"/>
    <tag group="fCategory" tag="Reserve"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Super"/>
    <tag group="SpecType" tag="SpellLike"/>
    <bootstrap thing="xResBonHea"></bootstrap>
    <eval phase="PostLevel" priority="5000"><![CDATA[~If the Conjuartion Healing CL Thing found then do
if (hero.childlives[zzConjHeal] <> 0) then
  ~ Add one to Conjuration Healing Caster Level
  hero.childfound[zzConjHeal].field[Value].value += 1
endif]]></eval>
    <prereq message="Ability to cast 2nd level spells required.">
      <validate><![CDATA[validif (tagcount[Hero.Divine] >= 2 + 1)
validif (tagcount[Hero.Arcane] >= 2 + 1)]]></validate>
      </prereq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fUmbralSh" name="Umbral Shroud" description="You control darkness and shadow.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 3rd-level spells.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have a 3rd-level or higher darkness spell available to cast, shadows and darkness appear to obey your will. As a standard action, you can direct these shadows to obscure the vision of one foe within 30 feet. If your target fails a Will save, its attacks have a miss chance equal to 5% per level of the highest-level darkness spell you have available to cast. This effect lasts until the beginning of your next action.\n\nCreatures that do not rely on sight are unaffected by this effect, and those with Blind-Fight or similar abilities can fight as they normally would.\n\nAs a secondary effect, you gain darkvision out to 10 feet. If you already have darkvision, its range increases by 10 feet.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="Feat" summary="Dark spl 3rd+, standard, foe in 30 ft has spl lvlx5% miss ch for 1 rd (Will neg)." uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Pre req(Done)

Set darkvision (done) Test? (Done)

