  <thing id="xMagDevote" name="Magic Devotion" description="You channel your faith into a bolt of energy that strikes your target form afar.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Once per day as a standard action, you can launch an energy bolt as a ranged touch attack against a target within 30 feet, +5 feet per two character levels you possess. If this attack hits, it deals 1d6 points of damage per two character levels you possess.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You can select this feat multiple times, gaining one additional daily use each time you take it.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: If you have the ability to turn or rebuke undead, you gain one additional daily use of this feat for each two daily turn or rebuke uses you expend." compset="Special" summary="X/day, standard, Y ft ranged touch does Zd6 dam." uniqueness="unique">
