  <thing id="cMExImGLea" name="Imdastri&apos;s Gift, Least" description="As an immediate action, you can reroll one attack roll, save, or check per day, as if using the granted power of the Luck domain (PH 187). This effect occurs instantaneously.\n\nEach paragon&apos;s gift (least, lesser, greater, and supreme) requires a swift action to invoke, lasts for a number of rounds equal to your mythic exemplar level, and is usable once per day. Abilities that indicate &#147;as the spell&#148; require a swift action to use regardless of the spell&#146;s normal casting time." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Immediate action, 1/day reroll one attack, save or check." uniqueness="unique">
