  <thing id="cOrCDivBul" name="Divine Bulwark" description="At 3rd level, you can sacrifice a prepared spell or spell slot as a swift action to gain damage reduction. The value of the damage reduction equals 1 + spell level sacrificed, and it can be overcome by a chaotic aligned strike. Thus, a 3rd-level ordained champion who sacrificed a {i}flame strike{/i} spell would gain damage reduction 6/chaotic for 3 rounds. The damage reduction gained from multiple uses of this ability does not stack. This protection lasts for a number of rounds equal to your ordained champion level." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Swift, gain DR/chaotic equal to 1 + spell level sacrificed for X rounds.">
    <comment>Page 91 &#150; Divine Bulwark
[Substitution]
(Su) should follow the class feature
name, not (Sp).</comment>
