  <thing id="cParApostl" name="Paragnostic Apostle" description="&quot;{i}If knowledge is power, omniscience is omnipotence. When we understand the nature of the world, we become its masters.{/i}&quot;\n&#151;Pallavarta Santalieri, Master of the Unturned Page\n\n{b}Special{/b}: Must be a member of the Paragnostic Assembly\n\nThe Paragnostic apostles are the most devoted of the Paragnostic Assembly (Complete Champion pg 72)&#151;the most erudite of a sect dedicated, mind and soul, to the acquisition of knowledge. These eminent scholars use the secrets they&apos;ve learned to augment their spells, and to shape the world around them it ways that other casters cannot. Knowledge is indeed power and the Paragnostic apostle understands that power better than most.\n\n{b}BECOMING A PARAGNOSTIC APOSTLE{/b}\nWizards, clerics, and archivists are best suited to this prestige class because of their skills and spellcasting progressions. However, bards, druids, sorcerers, favored souls (Complete Divine), and warlocks (Complete Arcane) sometimes follow this path as well. A high Intelligence score is essential because of the Knowledge skills required.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="ClassLevel" maxlimit="5">
    <fieldval field="cHitDice" value="4"/>
    <usesource source="CompChamp" parent="p35" name="Complete Champion"/>
    <tag group="ClassType" tag="Prestige"/>
    <bootstrap thing="cHelpPaA"></bootstrap>
    <link linkage="helper" thing="cHelpPaA"/>
    <exprreq message="Knowledge (arcana) 5 ranks required."><![CDATA[#skillranks[kKnowArcan] >= 5]]></exprreq>
    <exprreq message="Knowledge (religion) 5 ranks required."><![CDATA[#skillranks[kKnowRel] >= 5]]></exprreq>
    <prereq message="Able to cast 3rd-level spells required.">
      <validate><![CDATA[validif (tagcount[Hero.Arcane] >= 3 + 1)
validif (tagcount[Hero.Divine] >= 3 + 1)]]></validate>
      </prereq>
    <prereq message="Knowledge (any other) 5 ranks required.">
      <validate><![CDATA[ validif (#skillranks[kKnowArcEn] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowDun] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowGeog] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowLocal] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowHist] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowNat] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowNoble] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowPsi] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowPlane] >= 5)
 validif (#skillranks[kKnowOther] >= 5)]]></validate>
      </prereq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cPaAHoText" name="Holy Texts" description="Because of your study of sacred writings, your Paragnostic apostle levels stack with other class levels for the purpose of turning or rebuking undead and level-dependent domain abilities. You do not gain such abilities if you do not already have them, however." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Paragnostic Apostle levels stack for turn/rebuke undead and domain powers.">
