    </thing>
  <thing id="cImmBlind" name="Immunity to Blindness" description="Beginning at 2nd level, you cannot be blinded by magical effects, spells, or bright light. Physical barriers to sight, such as blindfolds and solid objects still prevent you from seeing. Additionally, any wounds that cause the destruction of your eyes still blind you." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Immune to magic or light blinding effects, destruction of eyes still blinds.">
