  <thing id="cPersEcl" name="Personal Eclipse" description="Beginning at 4th level, you can manipulate the direction and intensity of light. As a swift action, you can redirect the light around your body to better conceal your presence. Doing so grants you a circumstance bonus equal to one-half your Shadowspy level on Hide checks. This ability can be used at will but is effective only in areas where light is present." compset="ClSpecial" summary="At will redirect light to give circ bonus of 1/2 shadowspy level on Hide checks.">
