  <thing id="cSqLDaPath" name="Dardallion&apos;s Path" description="Upon becoming a squire of legend, you must choose one of the legendary Six from Shadow after whom to model your skills and abilities. Once made, your choice cannot be changed." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Followers of Dardallion have good Reflex saves and focus on luck and mobility." uniqueness="unique">
