  <thing id="xMantBeast" name="Mantle of the Beast" description="The {i}mantle of the beast{/i} allows you to use your wild shape ability as a swift action. While wild shaped, your natural weapons gain a +1 enhancement bonus on attack and damage rolls, giving you a magic weapon for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.\n\nA {i}mantle of the beast{/i} is part of a set known collectively as the {i}trappings of the beast{/i}, which also includes the {i}armor of the beast{/i} (page 135) and the {i}ring of the beast{/i} (see below). When you wear all three items together, you gain additional abilities, as noted in the description of {i}armor of the beast{/i}." compset="Special" summary="Wild shape as swift action, +1 enh bon to att &amp; dam for nat weapon in wild shape.">
