  <thing id="cvBearTot" name="Spiritual Totem: Bear" description="Barbarians who follow a spiritual path are often tied at some deep level to the wildlands that gave them birth. Such characters feel a kinship with the spirits of nature&#151;especially animal spirits&#151;and draw their power from these essences. Divine barbarians are viewed with awe and sometimes fear by their tribes, and some such characters are considered holy people in the absence of any organized religion.\n\n{b}Replaces{/b}: This benefit replaces the fast movement class feature.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain one of the abilities described below, depending on the chosen totem. Each of these effects is a supernatural ability.\n\n{b}Bear Totem{/b}: The mighty bear is known for her crushing embrace, if you adopt her as your spiritual totem, you gain the improved grab ability (MM 310).\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
