  <thing id="cvFriEvade" name="Friend&apos;s Evasion" description="By giving up one of your high-level special abilities, you&apos;ve learned to protect others by using your own skills and abilities.\n\n{b}Replaces{/b}: This benefit replaces improved evasion as one of the rogue&apos;s special ability choices.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When you select friend&apos;s evasion as a special ability, every ally adjacent to you gains evasion. This is an extraordinary ability.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Champion" compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
